box = [5.29589528, 295.29859815, 21.9582059]
box_mod = [b for b in box]
box_mod[0] = box_mod[0] + 0.001
caught_none = False
try:
    _check_box(None, None)
except ValueError:
    caught_none = True
assert caught_none
caught_diff = False
try:
    _check_box(box, box_mod)
except ValueError:
    caught_diff = True
assert caught_diff
box_ = _check_box(box, box)
assert np.allclose(box_, box)
box_ = _check_box(None, box)
assert np.allclose(box_, box)
box_ = _check_box(box, None)
assert np.allclose(box_, box)
